name: BCNMCR Letter B - Lamosca
description:
BCNMCR is a collection of letters created by design agencies Mayuscula, Hey, LoSiento, Mucho and Lamosca as well as by designer Dave Sedgwick. Designed initially to promote BCNMCR - an exhibition and event held in February 2013 in Manchester. Available to buy as individual letters or as a set of all 6. Profits will go directly to the MS Society.

Limited edition - 1 of 100

Letter B - From Lamosca 
A ballad to Mark B Smith, a fictional representation of the antithesis to Mark E Smith from The Fall. Beautifully illustrated and full of humour and wit. This piece is a must for all fans of the Manchester music scene and illustration!

A3 sized (29.7 x 42cm)

Giclée print on IFA24 Décor smooth art 210gsm paper

All 6 prints are available to buy together for £100 + postage. Please email shop@2022nq.co.uk if you wish to buy all 6

name: Ed Baptist - Up There
description:
Ed Baptist started his design life in advertising. His journey has taken him from advertising to retail with brief stints in the worlds of FMCG, type design and fashion. Some of his logo work has been featured in Lurzers Archive and Creative Review. 

He collected from friends, their favourite proverbs and words of wisdom, and compiled them into a collection called ‘Words of Wisdom’.

A3 sized (29.7 x 42cm)

Giclée print on IFA24 Décor smooth art 210gsm paper
